description: God, Sex and Truth is a 2018 film directed by Ram Gopal Varma starring an American pornographic actress Mia Malkova. The film is a short documentary about sex. The script is allegedly copied from Sarkar 3 writer P Jaya Kumar and upon his copyright claim the video has been taken down by Youtube. The film music is scored by M. M. Keeravani, who was known as MM Kreem for his Hindi compositions. The film is produced by Strike Force LLC, USA. It was released on January 27, 2018 on Vimeo OnDemand. Running Time: 19:20 minutes
